title: Claudia López
text:
Hi there! I am Claudia López, a Senior Data Engineer with a degree in Computer Science. I possess strong experience in Software Engineering and I am committed to continuous learning and staying up-to-date.
I created this blog to share my knowledge, findings and experiences about Software Engineering, Data Engineering, Machine Learning, and other interesting aspects of my professional journey.
